snippet.title: Lumi Trek - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3363410/Lumi_Trek/

We are happy to announce Lumi Trek, a rhythm-based casual game in which the colors of the stars can be changed by combining the three basic colors of light. Embark on a journey full of beautiful colors and great music!
